              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36903137/" class="">忽悠秦国</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/arielstillalive/" class=" " title="焦虑症患者">焦虑症患者</a>
                (还活着...)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36903137">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">杀人，往往不取决于实力，而取决于杀心。

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-03 11:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                杀人，往往不取决于实力，而取决于杀心。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
